00:08:26.190 --> 00:08:26.790
Off you go.

00:08:27.630 --> 00:08:28.310
Cut it out.

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:29.040
Yes, sir.

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:31.520
Sixth Prince,

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:34.039
