00:12:20.360 --> 00:12:21.510
Then why are you messing around here?

00:12:21.510 --> 00:12:22.080
Off you go.

00:12:22.080 --> 00:12:22.790
Old Master Hu!

00:12:22.790 --> 00:12:24.510
